Esitatimendeni esithunyelwe kwabezindaba izolo, inhlangano yamabandla ahlangane eKZN, ithe ifuna ukulekelela kulandela ukuba uMengameli Cyril Ramaphosa ememezele ukuvalwa kwezwe inyanga yonke. Bathe bayazi ukuthi uthaqa uzoba nemiphumela engemihle kwezomnotho kanjalo nakubantu abampofu. Bathe ukudla kuzoshoda kubantu abampofu. Bancome ubuholi bukaRamaphosa, iKhabhinethi noNdunankulu. “Siyakuncoma ukuba abaholi banikele ngengxenye yomholo wabo ukuze balekelele esikhwameni esizolekelela abantu nezinhlaka ezehlukene kulesi sikhathi. Sifisa ukuveza ukuthi amabandla ase-KZN nawo afisa ukunikela ngo-R1 million ukuze kulekelelwe esikhwameni sesifundazwe,” kusho isitatimende. Usihlalo we-KZN Church Leaders Group ophinde abe ngusihlalo we-KZN Inter Religious Council uCardinal Wilfrid Napier uthe: “Elakuleli livaliwe kuze kuphele * -Ephreli ngenxa yeCorona. Lokhu kuzoba nomthelela eongemuhle ikakhulukazi odabeni lokudla,” Ngaphansi kwalolu hlelo lokunikela, le nhlangano yamabandla izonikela ngama-voucher okudla komasipala besifunda abangu-11 e-KZN. Lama-voucher okudla azosebenza kunoma iziphi izitolo ezilandelayo, ika-Shoprite, Pick * Pay, Usave, Checkers noma kwaBoxer. Eminye imizamo yabo yokunikela kubalwa ukuxhumana nabantu nokufundisa ngegciwane, ukunakekela abefundisi, nokubheka umphakathi wonkana. Ngaphezu kwalokhu bathe kumele imikhuleko ingami. Kulo mkhankaso bahlangene ne-South African Council of Churches and Intellimali. Banxuse noma ubani ofisa ukufaka isandla ngalesi sikhathi enze njalo njengoba uMengameli eshilo ukuthi wonke umuntu angalekelela ukulwa neCorona.